[Business Merger Plan]

34
00:01:50,130 --> 00:01:56,000
[Company Name: Luquan Group; Representative: Lu Kuang-hsiang, Chairman; Company Name: Poseidon Department Store; Representative: Liang Wun-sen, Managing Director]

35
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:03,970
Why are you not signing it? These were all previously discussed.

36
00:02:03,970 --> 00:02:07,220
Do you have any other conditions to add?

37
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:09,520
Not really.

38
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:12,439
But you are the Vice Chairman of Poseidon Department Store,

39
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,940
don't you think it's inappropriate for you

40
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:17,400
to work brazenly for Luquan Group like this?

41
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:24,449
No matter what, Luquan Group will soon take over Poseidon Department Store.

42
00:02:24,450 --> 00:02:29,610
I'm just making preparations in advance.

43
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:35,640
When you do this, don't you feel guilty toward the late Chairman?

44
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,249
Don't take it wrongly.

45
00:02:37,249 --> 00:02:40,450
I'm doing him a favor by protecting Poseidon Department Store.

46
00:02:40,450 --> 00:02:44,690
He would appreciate what I'm doing for him in Heaven.

47
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,480
Are you sure?

48
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:54,540
You—... What are you doing here?

49
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:56,950
I'm here for a good show.

50
00:02:56,950 --> 00:03:00,260
Lawyer Shen, you are a witness too.

51
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:07,530
Liang Wun-sen, you—... What are you doing?

52
00:03:07,530 --> 00:03:11,830
Thank you, Vice Chairman Wu, for providing us with irrefutable evidence.

53
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:14,430
Give it back to me!

54
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,079
Liang Wun-sen, what the hell?

55
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:21,620
You are a wolf in sheep's clothing!

56
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:27,990
You are the one who is in "sheep's clothing."

57
00:03:27,990 --> 00:03:31,740
You are also the "wolf" who fails.

58
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,049
Wu Chang-shan!

59
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:37,830
I officially inform you that you are fired.

60
00:03:37,830 --> 00:03:42,929
Within the company's rights, Poseidon will file a lawsuit against you for compensation.

61
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:04,170
Seriously? Okay. I understand.

62
00:04:05,110 --> 00:04:07,280
We've all misunderstood Managing Director.

63
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,300
What do you mean?

64
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:14,300
So everything he did...

65
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:18,020
was to protect Poseidon.

66
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:20,840
He went undercover beside Vice Chairman Wu,

67
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:24,430
in order to get the evidence of his betrayal.

68
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:27,650
Do you know where Managing Director is now?

69
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:29,800
I don't know.

70
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,300
I need to take this afternoon off.

71
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:34,080
Lin Huai-en!

72
00:04:44,610 --> 00:04:48,660
[Tomb of Beloved Father Hai Yang]

73
00:04:56,340 --> 00:05:00,040
We successfully revealed Wu Chang-shan's true colors.

74
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:04,750
My dad would be feeling gratified in Heaven.

75
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:08,960
I believe we will make the company better when we work together.

76
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:14,330
Yes. We pretended to fight against each other.

77
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:16,529
You pretended to laze around.

78
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:20,850
We were certainly good actors.

79
00:05:20,850 --> 00:05:24,570
That's how we could get that trickster, Wu Chang-shan.

80
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:28,370
I remember that time when I was abroad,

81
00:05:28,370 --> 00:05:31,480
my credit card was suspended all of a sudden, I—

82
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:40,400
"Hai Yang has financially cut off Hai Yi. He's not useful anymore."

83
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:44,430
Let's break up. I'll get this bill.

84
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:48,340
- Lu Si-chi, what do you mean?
- Hello.

85
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:50,740
- I'm at Ritz-Carlton.
- I...

86
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:52,660
Come and join me.

87
00:05:55,379 --> 00:05:58,449
"There's been a change of plan. Talk to you later."

88
00:06:02,470 --> 00:06:04,459
Sam, what happened?

89
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:06,339
Your suspicion was correct.

90
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:08,410
There have been dubious financial transactions

91
00:06:08,410 --> 00:06:10,840
between Wu Chang-shang and Luquan Group.

92
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:13,559
It's time to catch the mole.

93
00:06:13,559 --> 00:06:16,619
I didn't discover anything suspicious from Lu Si-chi though.

94
00:06:16,619 --> 00:06:19,379
What about my dad? Does he know?

95
00:06:19,379 --> 00:06:22,159
Chairman always trusts Wu Chan-shan.

96
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:25,249
I think we'll have to prove it to your dad.

97
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:28,060
We can use the fact that Dad just cut me off financially.

98
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,979
Let's think about what to do next.

99
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:32,020
Okay.

100
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:34,749
It's a good thing that Lu Si-chi Lu is a snob.

101
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:37,500
Otherwise, we couldn't have fooled her.

102
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:42,019
Thanks for working with me these days.

103
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:46,239
You helped me investigate Dai Zhe-ni and arranged accommodation and jobs.

104
00:06:46,239 --> 00:06:48,660
I ordered you around like an assistant.

105
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:51,609
It's nothing. Don't mention it.

106
00:06:51,610 --> 00:06:55,890
A powerful person like you had to laze around. It's more exhausting.

107
00:06:57,550 --> 00:07:02,040
It was more exhausting for you. Thank you, Sam.

108
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:05,529
Wu Chang-shan has sent people to follow us recently.

109
00:07:05,530 --> 00:07:09,760
We must be careful. Someone is here. I have to go now.

110
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,619
You should try your best to assist Chairman at this time.

111
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:15,160
How can you side with Vice Chairman Wu?

112
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:19,950
You really disappoint me.

113
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:24,149
You'll have it in three days.

114
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:25,980
Are you brushing me off?

115
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:32,340
Tell me. How do you want to be rewarded? I'll give you anything.

116
00:07:34,090 --> 00:07:37,010
- Really?
- Yes.

117
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:38,819
I would like to take a break.

118
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:41,690
Come on. "A break"?

119
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:46,790
After we sort things out, I'll definitely allow you to have extended leave.

120
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:50,960
I mean... I need a real break.

121
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:57,030
In order to side with you, Huai-en was suspicious of me.

122
00:07:57,030 --> 00:08:01,750
I'm mentally exhausted. I need a proper break.

123
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:03,930
Sorry.

124
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:08,639
Your decision making and performance abilities

125
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:10,829
are way beyond my expectations now.

126
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:14,520
I'm sure you will lead Poseidon to a better future.

127
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,500
I have faith in you.

128
00:08:20,530 --> 00:08:22,010
By the way...

129
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:27,410
Here... Chairman, I need your signature.
[Resignation Application]

130
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:34,150
What do you plan to do next?

131
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:40,540
I would like to refurbish my house by the sea,

132
00:08:40,540 --> 00:08:42,890
and do whatever I want to do.

133
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:49,400
I'll keep this for now.

134
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:52,770
After you've had enough rest, feel free to come back anytime.

135
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,580
Is this a new song you've composed?

136
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:58,049
I did it when I missed you and felt angry at you.

137
00:09:58,050 --> 00:10:01,620
One music note at a time.

138
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:04,400
It gradually became a song.

139
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:08,800
I'm sorry, Huai-en.

140
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:11,880
I should be the one to apologize.

141
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:14,960
I should be the one who trusts you the most.

142
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:17,850
However, I suspected you.

143
00:10:17,850 --> 00:10:19,339
It's my fault.

144
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:24,230
I had to hide it from you and lie to you, because I didn't want you involved.

145
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:29,970
Now, I can finally show you that I'm not disloyal.

146
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:34,380
Everything you did was for Poseidon Department Store.

147
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,640
I was an idiot.

148
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:42,150
It's okay. The past is in the past.

149
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:52,460
I have something for you.

150
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,990
What is it?

151
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,960
This is for you.

152
00:11:06,650 --> 00:11:09,000
What a special design.

153
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:13,250
*"&" is a connected form of the Latin "et."
(*ampersand symbol)

154
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:16,350
It's also a symbol for "and" in English,

155
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:19,920
meaning both are indispensable.

156
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:25,319
Legend has it that a soul weighs *21 grams.
(*from Dr. D. Macdougall's experiments in 1907)

157
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:30,320
Twenty-one grams also means the weight of life.

158
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:40,430
You've made my life complete.

159
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,920
Do you accept my apology?

160
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,740
Put it on for me.

161
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:06,150
This way, I am bound to you.

162
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:16,030
I also have something to tell you.

163
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:17,950
What is it?

164
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:25,659
I resigned.

165
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:29,910
Why? Please don't take what I said seriously.

166
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:32,069
Should I go explain to Chairman?

167
00:12:32,070 --> 00:12:36,180
No. It was my decision.

168
00:12:37,110 --> 00:12:41,690
I've worked for Poseidon for a long while. I'm tired.

169
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:45,849
Now, I want to do whatever I want to do.

170
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:50,010
But what about me if you've resigned?

171
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:53,200
I still have a lot to learn from you.

172
00:12:55,850 --> 00:13:00,170
You are doing a good job. You can work independently now.

173
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:03,280
What is your next plan?

174
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,540
It's a secret.

175
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:12,190
What? Tell me. What's your plan?

176
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:14,080
- Tell me. Come on.
- No.

177
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:17,070
Tell me. What's your plan?

178
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:22,320
I'll show you later, then you'll know.

179
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:24,460
May I?

180
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:48,370
[Poseidon Department Store]

181
00:15:48,370 --> 00:15:49,669
Congratulations, Chairman.

182
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:51,919
You not only rid the company of the mole,

183
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:54,339
you also had two successful two events,

184
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:57,070
"Cheerful Kam-a-tiam" and "Happy Family".
- Thank you.

185
00:15:57,070 --> 00:15:59,799
The credit belongs to all the staff.

186
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:01,899
Chairman is so young and modest.

187
00:16:01,900 --> 00:16:05,249
Thank you, Chairman and Ms. Hai Yin for your interview with us.

188
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,449
Thanks for your work.

189
00:16:06,450 --> 00:16:07,539
We'll go now.

190
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:09,250
Take care.

191
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,239
Not bad.

192
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,720
You were very convincing when facing the journalists for the first time.

193
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:19,950
Thank you, Aunt. You've worked hard these days too.

194
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:22,520
Things are getting on track at the company now.

195
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:25,560
It's time for you to look for your happiness.

196
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:27,200
Me?

197
00:16:28,430 --> 00:16:31,290
I've been observing Dai Zhe-ni these days.

198
00:16:31,290 --> 00:16:33,060
A favor?

199
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:35,500
Here's the thing.

200
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:38,099
I don't mind that you stay beside Hai Yi,

201
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:42,660
but I refuse to help you improve your relationship.

202
00:16:42,660 --> 00:16:44,510
It's not about that.

203
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:50,980
I'd like to ask you to set up blind dates for Hai Yi.

204
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:56,850
Why? What is it for?

205
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:02,820
For some reason,

206
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:06,440
I don't know when I'll leave Hai Yi.

207
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:10,180
I'm worried that if I leave,

208
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:13,790
he may feel lonely by himself.

209
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:18,140
I found out that he genuinely loves you,

210
00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:21,190
so I hope you two can be together.

211
00:17:23,330 --> 00:17:24,899
I thought you would not agree.

212
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:29,510
Come on! I'm not a fuddy-duddy.

213
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:31,510
Okay.

214
00:17:34,090 --> 00:17:35,370
[Cartoony World]

215
00:17:35,370 --> 00:17:37,729
You've come and talked to me a lot.

216
00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:41,110
Did something happen between you guys again?

217
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,689
I just realized that

218
00:17:42,690 --> 00:17:48,230
Hai Yi pretended to be lazing around on purpose.

219
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:52,660
He was hiding it very well.

220
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:57,660
Hai Yi has always wanted to carry Poseidon Department Store forward. It was built by his dad.

221
00:17:57,660 --> 00:18:03,170
I didn't know he carried such a great responsibility until now.

222
00:18:03,170 --> 00:18:07,550
"With great power comes great responsibility."

223
00:18:08,170 --> 00:18:12,110
Now I adore and admire him even more.

224
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:15,640
So cheesy! You've fallen in love with such a talented guy.

225
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:18,180
You must be very proud.

226
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:26,379
It is actually kind of driving us apart.

227
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:29,440
I thought he was forced to inherit the business.

228
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:33,430
Now I know how serious he is.

229
00:18:33,430 --> 00:18:36,909
There's no way he'll give up everything and come with me to my year.

230
00:18:36,910 --> 00:18:38,879
Don't go back then.

231
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:42,950
I have to. I need to take care of my grandma.

232
00:18:42,950 --> 00:18:46,050
What are you going to do?

233
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:50,250
Since we can't be together,

234
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:53,860
maybe I should keep some distance from him.

235
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:57,360
At least it'll be less painful for us both

236
00:18:57,360 --> 00:19:01,650
after I go back.

237
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:14,330
What a beautiful place.

238
00:19:14,330 --> 00:19:15,950
Right?

239
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:23,009
Look. I'm planning to set up a stage here.

240
00:19:23,010 --> 00:19:25,029
I'd like to refurbish this place,

241
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:28,220
and make it a bed-and-breakfast as well as a cabaret.

242
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:31,669
That sounds great. I like it very much.

243
00:19:31,670 --> 00:19:36,640
Great. You can often play your new songs here in the future.

244
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:40,050
They are not even songs.

245
00:19:40,050 --> 00:19:42,050
You are probably the only one who enjoys them.

246
00:19:42,050 --> 00:19:44,110
No way.

247
00:19:45,690 --> 00:19:48,330
I have high standards.

248
00:19:48,330 --> 00:19:50,910
They don't bore me at all.

249
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,970
You are the best.

250
00:20:02,810 --> 00:20:05,210
What a comfortable place.

251
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:11,760
I'm glad you like it, because I'm doing this for you.

252
00:20:48,530 --> 00:20:50,010
What has happened?

253
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:51,920
Nothing.

254
00:20:53,950 --> 00:20:56,420
I especially blocked out my agenda today,

255
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:59,020
so we can go shopping and watch a movie.

256
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:00,509
Aren't you happy?

257
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,280
I am happy.

258
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:08,180
Dai Zhe-ni, you're faking your smile. Do you think I don't know?

259
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:10,530
What's wrong?

260
00:21:10,530 --> 00:21:15,870
Fine. I didn't sleep well last night. I'm a bit tired.

261
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:18,840
Let's go. The movie is about to start.

262
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,970
Let's go.

263
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:37,460
What should I do? How should I explain to Grandma?

264
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:41,410
No matter what, we'll wait.

265
00:21:41,410 --> 00:21:43,230
He...

266
00:21:45,180 --> 00:21:49,250
Absolutely here.

267
00:21:49,250 --> 00:21:51,390
You can't fake it.

268
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:54,160
I'll go and save him!

269
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:56,440
I'll bring him back.

270
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:15,070
I want to watch the film.

271
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:21,330
Believe me.

272
00:22:21,330 --> 00:22:23,110
No matter if you are willing or not,

273
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:27,590
without you or not, this is my 22-year-old birthday gift to myself.

274
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:37,070
"There's a box in my room with my magazines in it."

275
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:41,260
"Would you help me organize them when you are free?"

276
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:17,460
[Thank you for Poseidon Department Store's sponsorship so I can learn piano. I hope you like first my song...]

277
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:23,020
Why does Managing Director have these cards?

278
00:23:31,090 --> 00:23:33,210
- Hello?
- Hello.

279
00:23:33,210 --> 00:23:35,840
Director Liu. This is Huai-en.

280
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,990
Hello Huai-en.

281
00:23:36,990 --> 00:23:42,010
I would like to ask you about my sponsor.

282
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:45,640
Actually he's also from Rende Orphanage.

283
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:48,220
Later, when he started working at Poseidon Department Store,

284
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:52,140
he kept sponsoring us, especially you.

285
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:56,020
He said it was because you are very similar to him.

286
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:14,510
What's the matter with you?

287
00:24:16,730 --> 00:24:19,560
Why are you so indifferent toward me?

288
00:24:20,210 --> 00:24:21,529
Is there someone else?

289
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:23,750
No. Don't make it up.

290
00:24:23,750 --> 00:24:26,379
What's wrong? You are definitely hiding something from me.

291
00:24:26,380 --> 00:24:27,750
I...

292
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:36,550
I just think that there's a huge gap between us.

293
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:40,390
We are from two different worlds.

294
00:24:57,370 --> 00:25:00,350
No matter how big the world is,

295
00:25:01,950 --> 00:25:03,840
you are the only one I need.

296
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:06,799
It's not enough...

297
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,970
I feel insecure,

298
00:25:08,970 --> 00:25:11,950
and I don't want a relationship like this.

299
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:16,800
Do you prefer me to be someone who is idle all the time?

300
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:21,149
I'm doing all this so as to give you a secure future.

301
00:25:21,150 --> 00:25:24,270
What if there's no future?

302
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:26,560
What's wrong with you?

303
00:25:33,290 --> 00:25:35,910
I don't want to wait anymore.

304
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:44,889
"Dai Zhe-ni, I have some news about your grandma."

305
00:27:44,890 --> 00:27:49,640
"Come to my studio at 2 p.m. tomorrow and we'll talk."

306
00:27:51,950 --> 00:27:55,610
Master Chang, what took you so long?

307
00:27:55,610 --> 00:27:57,860
Has anything happened to my grandma?

308
00:27:57,860 --> 00:28:00,820
It took me a while.

309
00:28:00,820 --> 00:28:03,070
I finally find out that

310
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:07,239
"Venus" is your grandma's guardian angel.

311
00:28:07,239 --> 00:28:09,110
- Venus?
- Venus.

312
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:10,559
- Really?
- Really.

313
00:28:10,559 --> 00:28:13,559
Whatever! She's the western God of Love, isn't she?

314
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:15,029
Did the God Emperor get it wrong?

315
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:18,550
I thought it would be *Mazu.
(*Chinese sea goddess)

316
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:21,710
The God Emperor never gets things wrong.

317
00:28:21,710 --> 00:28:25,459
Sorry, Master. Don't be upset. Please continue.

318
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:27,760
Because She is a western God,

319
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:31,029
that's why it took me a while, a long time.

320
00:28:31,030 --> 00:28:35,630
But don't worry. Luckily, I speak English.

321
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:38,990
So what has happened to my grandma?

322
00:28:38,990 --> 00:28:43,260
She has missed you and worked too much.

323
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:44,979
She's not well.

324
00:28:44,980 --> 00:28:46,430
What do you mean "not well"?

325
00:28:46,430 --> 00:28:48,839
Would you please tell me more about it?

326
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:51,429
"Mysteries of Heaven must not be revealed."

327
00:28:51,429 --> 00:28:54,180
Oh no...

328
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:56,709
You said you could send me back, right?

329
00:28:56,710 --> 00:28:59,510
You finally understand.

330
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:01,789
Sending you back is a good way.

331
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:04,879
I just checked Ho Bo-wei's birth date and time.

332
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:09,640
Tonight at 9 p.m. is the best timing.

333
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:12,390
- So soon?
- Never mind.

334
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:14,999
All right... No problem.

335
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,929
I'll be here at 9 p.m. tonight.

336
00:29:16,930 --> 00:29:19,739
How much should I pay you?

337
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:22,179
Let's not talk about money.

338
00:29:22,180 --> 00:29:24,329
It's my job to send you back.

339
00:29:24,330 --> 00:29:26,879
Just show up on time.

340
00:29:26,879 --> 00:29:28,729
Thank you, Master Chang.

341
00:29:28,729 --> 00:29:30,959
Don't worry, I'll be here on time.

342
00:29:30,959 --> 00:29:33,270
Take care.

343
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:42,220
No problem.

344
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:44,280
I look forward to working with you.

345
00:29:49,290 --> 00:29:51,029
Huai-en, it's good that you're here.

346
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:53,139
Take these two documents to the HR Department.

347
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:55,480
Okay. Sure.

348
00:29:56,160 --> 00:30:00,490
Chairman, I would like to say something.

349
00:30:00,490 --> 00:30:02,210
Go ahead.

350
00:30:02,210 --> 00:30:07,880
Chairman, after thorough consideration, I would like to resign.

351
00:30:09,630 --> 00:30:11,690
[Resignation Application]

352
00:30:17,010 --> 00:30:19,190
It's because of Wun-sen, right?

353
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:27,020
Managing Director has been the one who has taught and guided me,

354
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:30,230
so that I finally have goals and directions in my life.

355
00:30:31,010 --> 00:30:33,420
I've decided to stay by his side.

356
00:30:35,570 --> 00:30:38,120
Since you've thought it through,

357
00:30:38,120 --> 00:30:40,760
I have no reason to keep you here.

358
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:46,660
Go and pursue your happiness.

359
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:49,430
Thank you, Chairman.

360
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:53,329
I hope you and Dai Zhe-ni live happily ever after.

361
00:30:53,330 --> 00:30:55,220
You knew about it?

362
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:58,715
You are really good friends.

363
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:32,150
Good luck. Grow up nicely.

364
00:32:35,410 --> 00:32:37,890
♫  I just want to be more than friends ♫

365
00:32:37,890 --> 00:32:39,870
Liang Wun-sen!
♫  I just want to be more than friends ♫

366
00:32:39,870 --> 00:32:41,380
♫  I just want to be more than friends ♫

367
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:44,440
♫ Why are we holding back? ♫

368
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:49,150
♫ It’s not just a little bit ♫

369
00:32:49,150 --> 00:32:55,140
♫ I just want to be your boyfriend ♫

370
00:32:55,140 --> 00:32:58,900
♫ Give love a starting point ♫

371
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:02,360
Huai-en.

372
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:06,690
What are you doing here? Have you skipped work?

373
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:11,070
Now I know. I know everything.

374
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:18,970
You were that big brother who encouraged me.

375
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:24,790
You also sponsored me to study and to learn piano, right?

376
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:29,810
Why didn't you tell me? Why not?

377
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:34,429
Because...

378
00:33:34,429 --> 00:33:38,340
I wanted to have a pure relationship with you.

379
00:33:38,340 --> 00:33:41,330
I didn't want you to be with me

380
00:33:41,330 --> 00:33:43,930
because you thought you had to pay me back.

381
00:33:43,930 --> 00:33:47,610
I would like to have a sincere relationship with you.

382
00:33:47,610 --> 00:33:50,880
Of course, I sincerely like you.

383
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:53,420
That's good.

384
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:59,110
It doesn't matter who your sponsor was.

385
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:02,890
We are together now. That's what matters.

386
00:34:06,610 --> 00:34:09,390
Since my first day at work...

387
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:16,810
you've been in my mind the entire time and have never left it.

388
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:22,750
I resigned from Poseidon Department Store.

389
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:29,520
Why? Hasn't working at Poseidon always been your dream?

390
00:34:29,520 --> 00:34:32,640
You are my dream.

391
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:35,280
I want to be with you forever.

392
00:34:37,660 --> 00:34:40,340
I want to stay here with you.

393
00:34:41,162 --> 00:34:44,162
Write more beautiful songs.

394
00:34:46,113 --> 00:34:49,950
I want to build a home here with you,

395
00:34:49,950 --> 00:34:52,710
a home that belongs only to us.

396
00:34:54,310 --> 00:34:57,670
Wun-sen, I love you.

397
00:34:57,670 --> 00:35:03,680
♫  I just want to be more than friends ♫

398
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:06,720
♫ Why are we holding back? ♫

399
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:11,430
♫ It’s not just a little bit ♫

400
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:17,400
♫ I just want to be your boyfriend ♫

401
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:21,140
♫ Give love a starting point ♫

402
00:35:21,140 --> 00:35:22,460
I love you, too.

403
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:29,000
♫ This one-foot distance is a big adventure ♫

404
00:35:55,680 --> 00:36:00,580
Actually, the person I want to take with me the most,

405
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:02,650
is Hai Yi.

406
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:35,369
Hai Yi... traveling through time to meet you...

407
00:36:35,369 --> 00:36:40,320
has been the most magical and happiest thing in my life.

408
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:42,140
Thank you.

409
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:47,930
However, I can't leave my grandma there.

410
00:37:00,700 --> 00:37:02,460
Hai Yi...

411
00:37:06,930 --> 00:37:10,550
I love you so much.

412
00:37:22,740 --> 00:37:26,380
If it's possible in the next life,

413
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:30,220
we'll meet again in the same time and space, okay?

414
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:48,339
Chairman, have you seen Dai Zhe-ni?

415
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:50,879
Dai Zhe-ni hasn't slept well lately.

416
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:53,691
He asked for today off to rest at home. What's wrong?

417
00:37:53,691 --> 00:37:55,470
Look.

418
00:37:58,040 --> 00:38:00,229
"Momo, it was nice to meet you."

419
00:38:00,230 --> 00:38:03,670
"I hope to see you again."

420
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:07,849
He just sent me that message. It's weird.

421
00:38:07,850 --> 00:38:11,360
Also, he met a psychic.

422
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:13,190
"A psychic"?

423
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:15,619
He said the guy could return him to his year.

424
00:38:15,620 --> 00:38:17,940
He sounded excited.

425
00:38:25,050 --> 00:38:28,260
[Dai Zhe-ni]

426
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:42,220
It's almost time. Why is Ho Bo-wei not here yet?

427
00:38:43,130 --> 00:38:45,600
Has he changed his mind?

428
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:48,750
Or, has Hai Yi stopped him?

429
00:38:54,390 --> 00:38:57,810
Master Chang.

430
00:38:57,810 --> 00:39:01,850
Ho Bo-wei, you are finally here.

431
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:04,760
Sorry, Master Chang. I had too many things to pack.

432
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:07,339
Hurry up. We're running out of time.

433
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:10,159
All right. Where should I leave my luggage?

434
00:39:10,159 --> 00:39:11,659
Anywhere will do.

435
00:39:11,660 --> 00:39:16,259
Don't worry. When you go back, your luggage will go with you.

436
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:17,669
Really?

437
00:39:17,670 --> 00:39:20,620
Should I get you a luggage tag?

438
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:23,980
No. It's okay. I trust you.

439
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,199
What should I do now?

440
00:39:28,200 --> 00:39:31,970
What should you do? Sit in the middle.

441
00:39:32,930 --> 00:39:37,210
Face outward with your legs crossed.

442
00:39:37,210 --> 00:39:42,250
Put your hands on your knees with palms facing up.

443
00:39:43,530 --> 00:39:46,829
Sink your breath to your lower belly. Sit your tongue on the roof of your mouth.

444
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:49,180
Close your eyes.

445
00:39:49,180 --> 00:39:54,190
Clear your mind. Relax.

446
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:56,800
Do not fall asleep.

447
00:40:15,700 --> 00:40:17,250
[Fortune]

448
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:24,260
Hai Yi, watch out!

449
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:29,009
What if I leave one day and you don't know any life skills?

450
00:40:29,010 --> 00:40:30,970
How are you gonna survive?

451
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:39,060
"My dad is gone, and you don't care about me."

452
00:40:39,060 --> 00:40:43,150
"Everyone leaves me. It's okay. I don't care."

453
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:45,800
"It's not the first time anyway."

454
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:51,300
♫ Every corner ♫

455
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:55,230
♫ (I thought...) The painful wound has already healed ♫

456
00:40:55,230 --> 00:41:00,110
♫ (I also thought...) Pretending I don’t care ♫

457
00:41:00,110 --> 00:41:02,240
Hai Yi.

458
00:41:06,240 --> 00:41:11,890
Dai Zhe-ni, you can't go. You must wait for me.

459
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:18,800
Dai Zhe-ni.

460
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:23,610
Dai Zhe-ni, don't go. Dai Zhe-ni! Wait.

461
00:41:23,610 --> 00:41:26,960
Hai Yi? What are you doing here?

462
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:28,980
Listen to me.

463
00:41:28,980 --> 00:41:32,560
Your grandma has already passed away in 2000.

464
00:41:33,690 --> 00:41:35,829
This psychic is a liar.

465
00:41:35,830 --> 00:41:38,980
Don't listen to his nonsense.

466
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:43,399
You are a liar.

467
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:45,610
What happened?

468
00:41:46,610 --> 00:41:51,460
You said Jin-hua has passed away. How do you know?

469
00:41:52,750 --> 00:41:56,790
I knew it when I hired someone to investigate Ho Bo-wei.

470
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:00,960
If you go back, she's not even there.

471
00:42:02,580 --> 00:42:04,409
I almost succeeded.

472
00:42:04,410 --> 00:42:08,520
Is it God's will? Oh, God's will...

473
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:17,310
You said... Jin-hua is gone.

474
00:42:20,970 --> 00:42:24,440
Why...

475
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:32,150
Why did you ruin my last hope?

476
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:35,649
Dai Zhe-ni... Dai Zhe-ni...

477
00:42:35,650 --> 00:42:38,970
Wait, Dai Zhe-ni. Wait.

478
00:42:39,570 --> 00:42:41,759
Wait. Calm down.

479
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:44,805
Leave me alone. Go away.

480
00:42:44,805 --> 00:42:47,410
How can I leave you alone?

481
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:50,459
My grandma is gone.

482
00:42:50,460 --> 00:42:54,630
I have no family in this world anymore.

483
00:43:00,900 --> 00:43:03,010
You have me.

484
00:43:09,930 --> 00:43:12,200
Hai Yi...

485
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:17,330
When I think of my grandma worrying about me

486
00:43:17,330 --> 00:43:19,530
when she passed away,

487
00:43:19,530 --> 00:43:22,890
I'm in so much pain.

488
00:43:26,200 --> 00:43:28,640
It's all my fault.

489
00:43:30,620 --> 00:43:34,810
You have me... you have me.

490
00:43:37,390 --> 00:43:39,375
I'm right here.

491
00:44:02,180 --> 00:44:04,080
Stay here.

492
00:44:06,190 --> 00:44:08,430
Let me take care of you.

493
00:44:13,170 --> 00:44:14,770
I love you.

494
00:44:58,440 --> 00:45:02,480
Does my Jin-hua really live here?

495
00:45:05,980 --> 00:45:08,570
After I found out your grandma had passed away,

496
00:45:08,570 --> 00:45:10,830
I moved her ashes here.

497
00:45:12,210 --> 00:45:15,250
I always wanted to give Jin-hua a better house.

498
00:45:16,170 --> 00:45:20,150
At least she lives in a mansion now.

499
00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:24,540
Thank you.

500
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:40,430
Don't be sad.

501
00:45:42,620 --> 00:45:44,540
After moving her ashes here,

502
00:45:44,540 --> 00:45:49,670
I've visited regularly to tell her that her Ho Bo-wei is safe and doing well.

503
00:45:50,280 --> 00:45:54,240
I believe she must be at ease in Heaven.

504
00:45:58,080 --> 00:46:01,315
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

505
00:46:05,980 --> 00:46:08,540
I didn't want you to be sad.

506
00:46:09,370 --> 00:46:11,770
I didn't know how to tell you.

507
00:46:15,980 --> 00:46:17,790
Thank you.

508
00:46:17,790 --> 00:46:21,360
Thank you for everything you've done for me and my grandma.

509
00:46:26,240 --> 00:46:28,390
Let's go visit your grandma.

510
00:46:29,700 --> 00:46:33,300
I want to introduce you to my grandma.

511
00:46:44,810 --> 00:46:46,580
Dai Zhe-ni.

512
00:46:47,270 --> 00:46:51,150
Brother Fu-de? How have you been doing?

513
00:46:51,150 --> 00:46:53,980
Not bad. My performance is not satisfactory though.

514
00:46:53,980 --> 00:46:55,729
- "Performance"?
- Nothing.

515
00:46:55,729 --> 00:46:58,580
I work here as a caretaker now.

516
00:46:58,580 --> 00:47:00,630
What a coincidence.

517
00:47:00,630 --> 00:47:02,249
- Hello. I'm Hai Yi.
- Hello.

518
00:47:02,250 --> 00:47:03,870
Zhe-ni told me about you.

519
00:47:03,870 --> 00:47:07,560
You are the owner of Poseidon. I have heard a lot about you.

520
00:47:07,560 --> 00:47:11,350
You are the reason why I have poor performance.

521
00:47:15,850 --> 00:47:19,150
- What brings you here?
- We're here to visit my grandma.

522
00:47:19,150 --> 00:47:21,880
Let me lead the way.

523
00:47:21,880 --> 00:47:23,459
I'm more familiar with this place.

524
00:47:23,460 --> 00:47:27,220
It's good to have a witness to hear what you say to your grandma.

525
00:47:33,070 --> 00:47:34,120
[Memorial tablet of Ho-Lee Jin-hua]

526
00:47:34,120 --> 00:47:35,800
Jin-hua...

527
00:47:36,630 --> 00:47:39,490
your grandson is here to see you.

528
00:47:40,730 --> 00:47:43,520
How are you doing in Heaven?

529
00:47:51,430 --> 00:47:53,210
I'm sorry.

530
00:47:54,260 --> 00:47:56,280
I was unfilial.

531
00:47:57,440 --> 00:48:00,280
I didn't stay with you.

532
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:03,130
I didn't take good care of you.

533
00:48:13,340 --> 00:48:16,190
If you don't let go,

534
00:48:16,190 --> 00:48:18,920
your grandma can't rest in peace.

535
00:48:20,740 --> 00:48:23,110
Let me introduce you to my grandma.

536
00:48:23,110 --> 00:48:25,310
It will make her happy.

537
00:48:25,310 --> 00:48:27,540
Just say whatever you want.

538
00:48:27,540 --> 00:48:30,460
I believe she can hear you.

539
00:48:33,170 --> 00:48:35,280
I'm so happy.

540
00:48:35,280 --> 00:48:39,230
I finally get to see my grandson.

541
00:48:39,230 --> 00:48:42,810
He's getting more and more handsome now.

542
00:48:43,650 --> 00:48:46,590
I know the guy next to him.

543
00:48:46,590 --> 00:48:48,260
He has visited me often.

544
00:48:48,260 --> 00:48:50,930
When they are standing together,

545
00:48:50,930 --> 00:48:54,520
they look like superstars.

546
00:48:54,520 --> 00:48:58,980
Grandma, he's Hai Yi.

547
00:48:58,980 --> 00:49:01,910
You've probably seen him before.

548
00:49:01,910 --> 00:49:04,890
He's the one who moved you here.

549
00:49:06,490 --> 00:49:09,040
He finally brought me here today.

550
00:49:09,820 --> 00:49:15,550
I'd like to tell you that I'm with Hai Yi now.

551
00:49:15,550 --> 00:49:19,080
I'm very happy and blessed.

552
00:49:20,260 --> 00:49:22,720
Don't worry about me.

553
00:49:22,720 --> 00:49:26,010
Grandma, it's good to see you again.

554
00:49:27,010 --> 00:49:29,710
Dai Zhe-ni and I—... I mean Ho—

555
00:49:29,710 --> 00:49:33,060
No matter whether he's Dai Zhe-ni or Ho Bo-wei,

556
00:49:33,060 --> 00:49:35,480
I will take care of him,

557
00:49:35,480 --> 00:49:38,350
protect him, be there for him forever.

558
00:49:38,350 --> 00:49:42,500
Please do not worry.

559
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:46,950
All right. Under the witness of me and Grandma Jin-hua,

560
00:49:46,950 --> 00:49:51,760
may you be together forever, be of one mind forever, and be always in love.

561
00:49:55,180 --> 00:49:58,570
Stop! ... Stop.

562
00:49:59,420 --> 00:50:02,410
- What's wrong?
- If you want to do that ceremony,

563
00:50:02,410 --> 00:50:06,600
I suggest you do it after you leave this place.

564
00:50:36,980 --> 00:50:38,180
What happened?

565
00:50:38,180 --> 00:50:40,450
You look so handsome.

566
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:43,639
Sorry. I'm late.

567
00:50:43,640 --> 00:50:45,519
- Director Yeh.
- Yeh.

568
00:50:45,520 --> 00:50:47,850
Today is New Year's Eve. Traffic is jammed.

569
00:50:47,850 --> 00:50:49,990
It's okay.

570
00:50:53,230 --> 00:50:55,870
You've finally made up with each other.

571
00:50:56,710 --> 00:50:58,539
Thank you, Director Yeh, for your pep talk.

572
00:50:58,540 --> 00:51:01,640
Don't mention it. Wun-sen and I are never polite to each other.

573
00:51:01,640 --> 00:51:05,290
I came here right after he said he's buying me a meal.

574
00:51:05,290 --> 00:51:07,109
"Happy Family" was a successful event

575
00:51:07,110 --> 00:51:09,179
and gave Poseidon a good sales performance.

576
00:51:09,180 --> 00:51:11,859
I'm happy to treat you to more than one meal.

577
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:14,419
- No backing out!
- Sure thing.

578
00:51:14,420 --> 00:51:17,640
By the way, would you like to go to the countdown with us after the meal?

579
00:51:17,640 --> 00:51:18,930
Sure.

580
00:51:18,930 --> 00:51:21,380
It's New Year's Eve, but Fu Yung-chieh is doing

581
00:51:21,380 --> 00:51:24,620
