582
00:51:25,930 --> 00:51:30,460
That's why I'm alone. I can only be your "third wheel" then.

583
00:51:30,460 --> 00:51:34,450
It's okay. It doesn't happen often. I'll lend you this one day.

584
00:51:34,450 --> 00:51:38,130
Mr. Yeh Hsing-ssu, you have a visitor on the rooftop.

585
00:51:38,130 --> 00:51:40,570
