609
00:54:04,650 --> 00:54:09,540
Do you want to grow old with me, as we accompany each other for the rest of our lives?

610
00:54:10,200 --> 00:54:14,520
Say yes. Say yes. Say yes.

611
00:54:14,520 --> 00:54:17,220
